Disney Plus hotstar bug

#DisneyPlusHotstar #AUSvsSA #live https://t.co/7bU0OQyODZ

The "Original" part always bugs me when it comes to streamers like Disney Plus and Netflix. It makes it sound like they've made it/own it. I remember when (outside of the UK) Netflix referred to Happy Valley as a Netflix Original.

They should change it to "Exclusive".
@DisneyPlus when are y’all gonna put bug juice on Disney plus??? That needs to happen asap please
